DataElement.preferredName: Supplement Statistics Analysis Plan Version Identifier ISO21090.II.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A type of statistical analysis plan version that provides specification for additional analyses not included as part of the principal statistical analysis plan version. EXAMPLE(S): Additional analyses during clinical study report preparation, Response to regulatory request, Hypothesis generation, Pre-specified PK analysis plan, Analysis plan for sub-study or study addendum A unique symbol that establishes the identity of a version of the statistical analysis plan.
